{"prompt": "Generate a website for a local artist portfolio. The website should be artistic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Evelyn Reed - Artist Portfolio</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #800000; /* Deep Red */\n            --secondary-color: #A52A2A; /* Brown, complements red */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a; /* Dark background */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            color: #e0e0e0;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: #2a2a2a;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 4rem;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            background-color: #2a2a2a;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--brand-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-size: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .gallery {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .gallery-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            display: block;\n            border: 2px solid var(--brand-color);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .gallery-item img:hover {\n            transform: scale(1.03);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n            color: #ccc;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            background-color: #3a3a3a;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Evelyn Reed</h1>\n        <p>Exploring emotion through vibrant strokes.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n        <a href=\"#gallery\">Gallery</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About the Artist</h2>\n            <p>Evelyn Reed is a contemporary artist based in [Your City]. Her work is deeply inspired by the ephemeral nature of emotions and the raw beauty of the natural world. Using a palette rich in deep reds and earthy tones, Evelyn seeks to evoke a sense of passion, introspection, and connection in every piece.</p>\n            <p>Her journey into art began at a young age, nurtured by a fascination with storytelling and visual expression. Over the years, she has developed a unique style characterized by bold brushwork and a masterful use of color to convey complex feelings.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"gallery\">\n            <h2>Featured Works</h2>\n            <div class=\"gallery\">\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/800000/ffffff?text=Crimson+Dream\" alt=\"Crimson Dream Artwork\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/A52A2A/ffffff?text=Ember+Glow\" alt=\"Ember Glow Artwork\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/800000/ffffff?text=Scarlet+Whispers\" alt=\"Scarlet Whispers Artwork\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/A52A2A/ffffff?text=Ruby+Veins\" alt=\"Ruby Veins Artwork\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/800000/ffffff?text=Sunset+Fever\" alt=\"Sunset Fever Artwork\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x250/A52A2A/ffffff?text=Terra+Cotta+Soul\" alt=\"Terra Cotta Soul Artwork\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>For inquiries about purchasing artwork, commissions, or collaborations, please use the form below.</p>\n            <form class=\"contact-form\">\n                <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"6\" required></textarea>\n\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Evelyn Reed. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic smooth scrolling\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}